542351706fdbf56a","tid":844160,"uid":186765,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T07:52:19.000Z","msg":"但是我亦走不進你心裡頭<br />\n某夜親吻到似變了男女朋友<br />\n但是你從不愛拖手 只是放手進我衣袖<br />\n代表只想取暖 是否？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c6866f4054d81f5a4ab5824a6adf7666103e290","tid":844160,"uid":186765,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T07:59:08.000Z","msg":"而我想寫首法文歌叫「jamais」<br />\n「永遠不會」的意思<br />\n「jamais je ne t'ai dit que je t'aimerai toujour」<br />\n<strong>過了秋天　再過冬天<br />\n我都回不到你身邊</strong><br />\n然後這一首歌的最尾一句叫「adieu」<br />\n意思是「永遠的再見」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nI never told you that I will always love you<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5a47dc4382558982d1e1bb78f843f168340974f","tid":844160,"uid":206634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T11:21:42.000Z","msg":"あんなに側にいたのに まるで嘘みたい<br />\nとても忘れられない それだけが確か<br />\n<br />\n你曾是那麼近在咫尺 那般過往卻有如謊言<br />\n無論如何都忘不了你 唯有這點無庸置疑"},{"pid":"6e2fe17253f647b413794a2be4331d663325cdcf","tid":844160,"uid":140798,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c5a47dc4382558982d1e1bb78f843f168340974f","tid":844160,"uid":206634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T11:21:42.000Z","msg":"あんなに側にいたのに まるで嘘みたい<br />\nとても忘れられない それだけが確か<br />\n<br />\n你曾是那麼近在咫尺 那般過往卻有如謊言<br />\n無論如何都忘不了你 唯有這點無庸置疑"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T11:32:30.000Z","msg":"個八婆好鍾意lemon<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ef16506f75c07c8259b5757d664498a0d416c14","tid":844160,"uid":206634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6e2fe17253f647b413794a2be4331d663325cdcf","tid":844160,"uid":140798,"like":1,"disli